---
// Downloads page outside Starlight layout
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Downloads - Sharpee</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Download Zifmia game runner and Sharpee game files">
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      background: #f8fafc;
      color: #1e293b;
    }
    .header {
      background: #fff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
    }
    .header-content {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .back-link {
      color: #059669;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .back-link:hover { color: #047857; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: bold; color: #1e293b; margin-top: 0.25rem; }
    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }
    .logo-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .logo-header img {
      max-width: 320px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .logo-header p {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .section {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .section h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    .section .subtitle {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .download-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .download-card {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    }
    .download-card:hover {
      border-color: #059669;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(5, 150, 105, 0.1);
    }
    .download-card .icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .download-card .label {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
    .download-card .meta {
      color: #64748b;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    .note {
      background: #f0fdf4;
      border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      color: #166534;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-content">
      <div>
        <a href="/" class="back-link">&larr; Back to Sharpee</a>
        <h1>Downloads</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="logo-header">
      <img src="/images/sharpee-logo.png" alt="Sharpee" />
      <p>Interactive Fiction Engine for TypeScript</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Zifmia Game Runner</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Desktop application for playing Sharpee games (.sharpee files)</p>
      <div class="download-grid">
        <a class="download-card" href="/downloads/Zifmia_0.9.0_x64_en-US.msi">
          <div class="icon">&#x1f5a5;</div>
          <div class="label">Windows</div>
          <div class="meta">Zifmia 0.9.0 &middot; x64 MSI</div>
        </a>
        <a class="download-card" href="/downloads/Zifmia_0.9.0_aarch64.dmg">
          <div class="icon">&#x1f34e;</div>
          <div class="label">macOS</div>
          <div class="meta">Zifmia 0.9.0 &middot; Apple Silicon DMG</div>
        </a>
        <a class="download-card" href="/downloads/Zifmia_0.9.0_amd64.deb">
          <div class="icon">&#x1f427;</div>
          <div class="label">Linux</div>
          <div class="meta">Zifmia 0.9.0 &middot; amd64 DEB</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Game Files</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Download .sharpee game files to play in Zifmia</p>
      <div class="download-grid">
        <a class="download-card" href="/downloads/dungeo.sharpee">
          <div class="icon">&#x1f3f0;</div>
          <div class="label">Dungeon</div>
          <div class="meta">Mainframe Zork (1981) recreation</div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="note">
        Download a Zifmia installer above, then open the <code>.sharpee</code> file in Zifmia to play.
        You can also <a href="/play/dungeo/" style="color: #059669;">play Dungeon in your browser</a>.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
